Stefan uses emacs.  His Internet monicker is [::monnier].

Stefan has been a GnuEmacs developer since 1999.

Stefan is a faculty member at Université de Montréal in the Department of Data Processing and Operations Research.

Stefan is an agitating labor activist working with Graduate Employees and Students Organization (GESO).

